[Student "S"]
{NORTH bids 4\C after SOUTH's Jacoby 2NT. The reason for this bid is just to describe 
her hand as having a side 5-card \C suit. NORTH knows the eventual contract will 
be some level of \Hs.

SOUTH doesn't have a strong hand, but he would show \D control at 
this time if he had the Ace. He isn't strong enough to go past game to show the \SA, so he 
just bids 4\H.}

